Goal of the course is to give theoretical and practical skills in data visualization and communication of analysis results. During the course we provide overview of most important visualization methods, principles of visual design and application of those in desinging slidedecks, posters and dashboards.Objectives/eesmärkid:  Objectives for the course are: -introduce principles of data visualization - give overview on graphical options for data representation according to data types - develop practical skills on effective data visualisation - give overview of using diagrams and infographics to communicate data science results - introduce storytelling and design principles and applications on creating slides, posters and dashboardsLearning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Student knows and can apply principles of data visualization Student can find the best visualization for given dataset and also implement it in practice Student knows how and when to use interactivity  Student can create presentations, posters and dashboards using best design and storytelling practices.
